        {
            "title": "半日收市｜港股半日跌276點  晶片股挫  科技股拖低大市",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股半日跌276點，美國總統特朗普講講話令市場對美伊停戰希望落空，晶片股挫，科技股成跌市主力，吉利(00175)逆市大升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：吉利汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250902_FI_source-web_00175-3-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：吉利汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250902_FI_source-web_00175-3-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：吉利汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數半日跌276點或1.09%，報25017，今早低開39點或0.16%，報25254點，已為上午高位所在，美國總統特朗普講話後急向下，尾段低見25003，挫291點或1.15%，為半日低位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數跌104點或2.21%，報4651，恒生國企指數跌83點或0.98%，報8421點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交1161.97億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指跌295點或1.17%，報25003，低水14點 ; 科指期貨跌105點或2.21%，報4645點，低水7點 ; 國指期貨報8414點，跌89點或1.05%，低水7點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">晶片股挫，中芯國際(00981)跌4.73%，報50.35元，為表現最差藍籌股，華虹半導體(01347)瀉5.08%，報79.4元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科網股是拖累大市主力。阿里巴巴(09988)跌3.5%，報118.4元，拖累恒指65點；小米(01810)跌4.12%，報30.7元；騰訊(00700)跌1.65%，報488.4元 ; 美團(03690)跌3.11%，報79.4元；合共推低恒指93點；百度(09888)跌1%，報108.5元 ; 快手(01024)跌2.81%，報44.9元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">吉利汽車(00175)升6.46%，報23.4元，以半日高位收市，為3 年新高，旗下極氪3 月銷量按年大增90%，花旗升目標價至27元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15827436-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c276%e9%bb%9e-%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e6%8c%ab-%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e8%82%a1%e6%8b%96%e4%bd%8e%e5%a4%a7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-8.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 12:33:17",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "騰訊QQ接入OpenClaw  用戶可「養龍蝦」",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地傳媒道，騰訊(00700)QQ官方表示，QQ已正式原生接入OpenClaw官方平台，騰訊輕量雲協同QQ團隊貢獻的QQ Bot 碼已合入OpenClaw主倉庫。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2026/03/OpenClaw-Web1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2026/03/OpenClaw-Web1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地《快科技》報道，OpenClaw日前發布v2026.3.31新版本，更新內置QQ官方插件，騰訊稱這代表QQ正式接入接入OpenClaw平台。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報道指，內置QQ Bot插件支持qq私聊及多媒體消息交互，提供多帳號、憑證管理、Slash命令等，意味只要有QQ戶口，就可直接接入「小龍蝦」。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在部署方面，僅三步操作就可完成。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊表示，在QQ養龍蝦與平常聊天一樣，不用學複雜操作。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15827296-%e9%a8%b0%e8%a8%8aqq%e6%8e%a5%e5%85%a5openclaw-%e7%94%a8%e6%88%b6%e5%8f%af%e3%80%8c%e9%a4%8a%e9%be%8d%e8%9d%a6%e3%80%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-ap_China_Tencent_Group-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 12:13:24",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
