            "title": "A股半日跌   深股創板跌逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日收跌，美國總統特普講話後跌幅擴大，深股及創業板跌逾1%，兩市成交合計11866.74億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-11.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-11.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指半日收跌20點或0.53%，報3927點，早段高見3952點，升4點或0.1%，美國總統特朗普講話後拾級而下，低見3926，跌22點或0.56%，為半日低位，半日成交5164.81億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指半日跌158點或1.15%，報13548，最高見13680，跌26點或0.19%，尾段低見13541，跌165點或1.2%，半日成交6701.93億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日跌57點或1.78%，報3189點 ; 滬深300半日跌33點或0.74%，報4492點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15827231-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%89%b5%e6%9d%bf%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-10.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 11:56:57",
