        },
        {
            "title": "A股開跌   上證跌8點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證指數開報3940點，跌0.2%或8點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開報13658點，跌0.35%或48點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指開報3229點，跌0.55%或18點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300開報4514.44點，跌0.26%或12點。</p>\n</div>",
